(view source)La Bella Italia

This example map of Italy showcases some ways you can style Kartograph maps. The base colors are defined in CSS, glow filters and image textures are applied in SVG. Also you can see heavy use of symbols (labels and icons) as well as geo paths. The labels are set in the Aquiline font, created by Manfred Klein.
